https://nextjs.org/learn/excel/typescript/setup -- learn nextjs to typescript
https://nextjs.org/docs#typescript --- nextjs typescript documentation

******************************
$env:NODE_ENV="development" or "production" for windows 10 in powershell
setting in package.json --->  "build:ts": "webpack --config webpack.%NODE_ENV%.js"

******************************
launch typescript custom server:
1)npm run build:ts
2)npm run start:ts

include ignore next folders and files:
.next
dist
node_modules
next-env.d.ts
package-lock.json

*********DEPRECATED***********
launch typescript default server(from box):
1) npm run build
2) npm  start 
******************************

WARNING:
if you not use .env, you need delete parametrs "--require dotenv/config"
in package.json, block "scripts"